This is XQilla, a C++ implementation of XQuery and XPath 2.0 based on Xerces-C.

This repository contains code XQilla mercurial repository located at:
https://sourceforge.net/p/xqilla/xqilla/ci/default/tree/

Fiels are snapshot taken from default branch at 4.10.2023.

Build Instructions
------------------

1. Download a source distribution of Xerces-C 3.0.1
2. Build Xerces-C

cd xerces-c-3.0.1/
./configure
make

4. Build XQilla

cd xqilla/
./configure --with-xerces=`pwd`/../xerces-c-3.0.1/
make

